### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-org/ucbl-logger.git
cd ucbl-logger

# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev,eks]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/

# Run integration tests (requires Kubernetes)
pytest tests/integration/
```